My body mostly consists of...

13
00:00:50,759 --> 00:00:54,442
rice balls, salad,
and stuff in supermarkets.

14
00:00:56,623 --> 00:00:59,259
I have the same food

15
00:00:59,928 --> 00:01:02,229
